⚠️  ENCRYPTION KEY REQUIRED
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Marmot requires an encryption key to protect sensitive pipeline credentials.

To generate a key, run:
  marmot generate-encryption-key

Then set it via:
  export MARMOT_SERVER_ENCRYPTION_KEY="your-generated-key"

Or to run WITHOUT encryption (NOT RECOMMENDED):
  export MARMOT_SERVER_ALLOW_UNENCRYPTED=true

⚠️  Running unencrypted means pipeline credentials will be stored
    in PLAINTEXT in the database. This is a SECURITY RISK.
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
